petersburg , surgut , syktyvkar , tyumen , ufa , ulyanovsk , dan yekaterinburg .
destinasi_internasional :_aktau , almaty , ashgabat , baku , gyumri , istanbul , kiev , khisinev , munich , tbilisi , thessaloniki , yerevan .
